'''NGC 6744'''是位於[[孔雀座|孔雀座]]的一個[[中間螺旋星系|中間螺旋星系]]，距離[[地球|地球]]大約3,000萬[[光年|光年]] <ref name=ned-dist/>。它被認為是類似[[銀河系|銀河系]]的眾多螺旋星系中最接近的之一，有著絮結的 (蓬鬆的) 旋臂和細長的核心。它至少還有一個被扭曲的衛星星系 (NGC 6744A)，外觀上類似[[大麥哲倫星系|大麥哲倫星系]]<ref name=ned-NGC6744A>{{cite web
  |title=NASA/IPAC Extragalactic Database
  |work=Results for NGC 6744A
  |url=http://nedwww.ipac.caltech.edu/cgi-bin/nph-objsearch?objname=NGC+6744A&img_stamp=yes&extend=no
  |accessdate=2010-06-19
  |archive-date=2019-12-07
  |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191207175950/http://nedwww.ipac.caltech.edu/cgi-bin/nph-objsearch?objname=NGC+6744A&img_stamp=yes&extend=no
  |dead-url=no
  }}</ref>。

2005年在NGC 6744內發現一顆超新星<ref name="mobberley">{{cite book |title=The Caldwell Objects And How to Observe Them |first=Martin |last=Mobberley |authorlink=Martin Mobberley |pages=208–09|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=amPrWoOWgHcC&pg=PA208 |publisher=Springer |year=1999 |isbn=978-1-4419-0326-6}}</ref>。

NGC 6744是[[室女座超星系團|室女座超星系團]]的成員星系<ref name="fouqueetal1992">{{cite journal | author=P. Fouque | author2=E. Gourgoulhon | author3=P. Chamaraux | author4=G. Paturel| title=Groups of galaxies within 80 Mpc. II - The catalogue of groups and group members | journal=Astronomy and Astrophysics Supplement | date=1992 | volume=93 | pages=211–233 | bibcode=1992A&AS...93..211F}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://ned.ipac.caltech.edu/level5/Dev2/frames.html|title=Nearby Groups of Galaxies|website=ned.ipac.caltech.edu|access-date=2018-05-04|archive-date=2019-02-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190227015942/http://ned.ipac.caltech.edu/level5/Dev2/frames.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

